data.description: Step into the charm of Texas living with this gorgeous 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home that seamlessly blends traditional style with modern updates. This spacious haven boasts stainless steel appliances, laminate, tile, and carpet flooring, along with updated fixtures throughout. The master bathroom is a luxurious escape with a double vanity, garden tub, and an over-sized closet. Enjoy the expansive backyard with mature trees, and revel in the convenience of being minutes away from USAA, UTSA, Medical Center, Golf Club, OP Schnabel Park, and major highways. This home is a perfect blend of Texas elegance and contemporary comfort.
